<!-- services - diseases -->
<section class="w3l-bottom-grids-6 py-5" id="allservices">
    <div class="container py-lg-5 py-md-4 py-2">
        <h6 class="title-small text-center">Resource</h6>
        <h3 class="title-big mb-md-5 mb-4 text-center"> Playwrite Occupational Therapy </h3>
        <div class="grids-area-hny main-cont-wthree-fea row">
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 grids-feature mt-4">
                <div class="area-box">
                    <span class="fa fa-puzzle-piece"></span>
                    <h4>
                        <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Resources" asp-action="AutismSpectrumDisorder" class="title-head">
                            Autism Spectrum Disorder (ASD)
                        </a>
                    </h4>
                    <p>
                        A complex developmental condition related to brain development that impacts how a person perceives and socializes with others,
                        causing problems in social interaction and communication.
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 grids-feature mt-4">
                <div class="area-box">
                    <span class="fa fa-eye"></span>
                    <h4>
                        <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Resources" asp-action="SensoryProcessingDisorder" class="title-head">
                            Sensory Proccessing Disorder(SPD)
                        </a>
                    </h4>
                    <p>
                        A condition in which the brain has trouble receiving and responding to information that comes in through the senses.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 grids-feature mt-4">
                <div class="area-box">
                    <span class="fa fa-wheelchair"></span>
                    <h4>
                        <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Resources" asp-action="CerebralPalsy" class="title-head">
                            Cerebral Palsy
                        </a>
                    </h4>
                    <p>
                        A group of disorders that affect a person's ability to move and maintain balance and posture. CP is the most common motor disability in childhood.
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 grids-feature mt-4">
                <div class="area-box">
                    <span class="fa fa-hand-paper-o"></span>
                    <h4>
                        <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Resources" asp-action="DownSyndrome" class="title-head">
                            Down Syndrome
                        </a>
                    </h4>
                    <p>
                        A condition in which a person has an extra chromosome and can affect a person's cognitive ability and physical growth, can
                        cause mild to moderate developmental issues, and higher risk of some health problems
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 grids-feature mt-4">
                <div class="area-box">
                    <span class="fa fa-spinner"></span>
                    <h4>
                        <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Resources" asp-action="DevelopmentalDelay" class="title-head">
                            Developmental Delay
                        </a>
                    </h4>
                    <p>
                        Refers to a child who has not gained the developmental skills expected of him or her, compared to others of the same age.
                        Delays may occur in the areas of motor function, speech and language, cognitive, play, and social skills.
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 grids-feature mt-4">
                <div class="area-box">
                    <span class="fa fa-book"></span>
                    <h4>
                        <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Resources" asp-action="LearningDifficulties" class="title-head">
                            Learning Difficulties
                        </a>
                    </h4>
                    <p>
                        Indicate an individual's need for alternative learning methods, they are not indicative
                        of intelligence level and are not the same as intellectual difficulties—learning challenges that result from sensory handicaps;
                        developmental delays; or cultural, economic, or environmental disadvantages.
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
